# - Config file for the genbb_help package
# It defines the following variables
#  genbb_help_INCLUDE_DIRS - include directories for genbb_help
#  genbb_help_LIBRARIES    - libraries to link against
#  genbb_help_DEFINITIONS  - special compilation flags
#  genbb_help_WITH_DEBUG   - flag for debug mode
# If Boost/Serialization I/O system is supported :
#  genbb_help_WITH_BIO     - flag for Boost/Serialization I/O DLL (a.k.a. 'bio')
# If Boost/Python wrapper module is supported :
#  genbb_help_WITH_PYTHON_WRAPPER - flag for 'Boost/Python' module 

